{"tid":1779282,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【燥到爆】幾時先學識靜靜雞啊屌你？","createTime":"2019-12-11T14:27:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T14:32:14.000Z","uid":177082,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"011a2d37d38c481d55ec10edbe1ec8ee5c48ee7f","tid":1779282,"uid":177082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T14:27:50.000Z","msg":"啱啱準時10pm係屋企大家如常係度嗌口號<br />\n<br />\n樓下公園有班細路無啦啦大嗌<br />\n<br />\n細路：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：嗌口號有咩用啊 唔好阻住人訓啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：日日都係咁嗌㗎啦 何況你自己都未訓<br />\n<br />\n（跟住其他人繼續嗌）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：嗌口號有咩用啊 遊行你地又唔黎！得80萬咋 100萬都無 ！<br />\n我有被人拉過啊 你呢有無吖？<br />\n遊行你地又唔出 我地嗰日先行完啊 你地呢？<br />\n見唔見到我地著緊黑衫啊 我地啱啱先去完啊！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：屌你收聲啦 無人想知啊 我做咗啲咩唔洗同你交代 識唔識靜靜雞啊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好撚燥 手足可唔可以俾啲警覺性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我呢區可謂全港數一數二最藍<br />\n藍到凌晨貼文宣 日出前就會被人撕嗰種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢個屋苑所有保安都係藍<br />\n日日都同啲藍絲吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要公園好應聲 佢地就咁傾計 我唔係頭三層都聽得好清楚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家佢地係樓下講緊班狗點點點咁<br />\n<br />\n屌 係咪想被人拉啊<br />\n警覺性呢？？？"},{"pid":"27438524740fe88d269f4bf113a59bbd56ffb0ff","tid":1779282,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T14:29:02.000Z","msg":"努力打好國際線<br />\n今日香港都成為美加焦點<br />\n<br />\n 【Twitter要人!!】美加議員人權日tweet集合list!!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1779138\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1779138</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">需要人入去推post<img src=\"/ass